In a mixing bowl, toss together the peas, cucumbers, carrots, cabbage, pepper, and scallions. In a small mixing bowl, whisk together the vinegar and olive oil. Lightly crush the mustard seeds in a mortar with a pestle and add to the oil and vinegar. Add the paprika and salt, if using, whisk well, and drizzle over the salad. Toss well and serve immediately. Garnish with parsley.